---
slug: "track"
permalink: "/es/track/index.html"
title: "Seguimiento del viaje · Demo | Morrison Premium Transfer"
description: "Demostración de la página de seguimiento del transfer en tiempo real."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Seguimiento", path: "/es/track/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker">{{ t.trackPage.eyebrow }} · DEMO</p>
    <h1>{{ t.trackPage.title }}</h1>
    <p class="lead">{{ t.trackPage.lead }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--bg-soft">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="track-card" data-track-card>
      <div class="track-status">
        <span class="track-dot"></span>
        <span data-track-status>{{ t.trackPage.statusOnRoute }}</span>
      </div>
      <h2>GRU → Campinas</h2>
      <p class="muted">{{ t.trackPage.routeLabel }}</p>

      <div class="track-progress">
        <div class="track-progress-bar"><span data-track-bar style="width: 0%"></span></div>
        <div class="track-progress-meta">
          <span class="num"><span data-track-percent>0</span>%</span>
          <span class="muted small">{{ t.trackPage.etaLabel }}: <span class="num" data-track-eta>--:--</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <dl class="track-grid">
        <div>
          <dt>{{ t.trackPage.driverLabel }}</dt>
          <dd>Carlos M.<br><small class="muted">CNH D · 8 años · EN B2</small></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>{{ t.trackPage.vehicleLabel }}</dt>
          <dd>Toyota Corolla Altis<br><small class="muted">Sedan ejecutivo · GRU-•••• <span class="muted">demo</span></small></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>{{ t.trackPage.statusLabel }}</dt>
          <dd class="num" data-track-distance>23 km al punto de retiro</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>

      <div class="track-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ t.trackPage.contactDriver }}</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ t.trackPage.contactSupport }}</a>
      </div>

      <div class="track-ar">
        <div class="track-ar-qr" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" width="80" height="80">
            <rect width="80" height="80" fill="#fff"/>
            <g fill="currentColor">
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="20" height="20"/><rect x="8" y="8" width="12" height="12" fill="#fff"/><rect x="12" y="12" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="56" y="4" width="20" height="20"/><rect x="60" y="8" width="12" height="12" fill="#fff"/><rect x="64" y="12" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="4" y="56" width="20" height="20"/><rect x="8" y="60" width="12" height="12" fill="#fff"/><rect x="12" y="64" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="6" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="6" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="46" y="6" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="14" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="42" y="14" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="22" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="22" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="46" y="22" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="6" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="14" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="30" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="50" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="58" y="30" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="70" y="30" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="22" y="38" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="30" y="38" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="46" y="38" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="62" y="38" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="6" y="46" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="14" y="46" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="30" y="46" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="46" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="54" y="46" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="58" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="58" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="46" y="58" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="66" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="42" y="66" width="4" height="4"/>
              <rect x="30" y="74" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="38" y="74" width="4" height="4"/><rect x="46" y="74" width="4" height="4"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="track-ar-copy">
          <p class="kicker">AR · en desarrollo</p>
          <p>En un viaje real, este QR abrirá el punto de retiro directamente en la cámara del teléfono — sin buscar edificio ni puerta.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="muted small" style="margin-top: 1.4rem; text-align: center;">{{ t.trackPage.demoNote }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
